Reclusa::

She gave him a shocked look. "I beg your pardon! I never said that you
were low ranking or even thought it. I did say that your leader
wouldn't have sent any less than one of his best bots for me. And, by
your own emmission, you are one of his best. But I am glad to hear
that your are a widely diversified bot who's skills are most
invaluable. I am glad to see that your not only a great warrior, but a
science bot as well."  She turned and faced the doors. "I am pleased
that you were choosen to escort me here. I have every confidence that
you are the bot to come to should any problems arise."  She turned to
face him, "I would also expect that you are the best bot to talk to
about a few up-grades. Not that I have any deficencies.  But I would
lke to see any personal weapons upgrades you may have to offer."
